    "created_at": "2019-02-03T17:10:25Z",
    "updated_at": "2019-02-03T17:10:25Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I'm all for consistency. And the engine is clearly laying them out left-to-right. In the case of `Record bookmark` and `Jump to bookmark`: these are corresponding pairs of hotkeys which - when you look at it that way - are also layed out left-to-right. Changing the order to top-to-bottom would require changing how the rendering for the fields works. And that is out of scope here. This PR's only aim is to bring the order in line with the stance bar (`Attack Anything`, `Defend`, `Return Fire`, `Hold Fire`) :-)"
  },
